version_description:
• Addition of Loan Payment Amount and Due Date fields
• Additional security enhancements and bug fixes

- Fix for jailbroken phones crashing on app startup.
- Minor enhancements and bug fixes.

– Touch ID support for log in
– Connect with us through our Secure Message Center
– Minor bug fixes

– Security enhancements
– This is a mandatory upgrade to all users due to the cloud security upgrade

- Added Enroll capability on Login screen
- Added announcement popup after login
- Added SWIPE gesture on Account Summary for quick navigation to Transfers/Payments/Deposits with pre-filled from/to account
We noticed a small issue with our last release. This version will fix that. Thank you for being a Partners Member!

The newest version (v7.0.1) of Partners Mobile Banking offers more than ever! We've listened and the latest update gives you a new look and feel, making it easier and quicker to use our app:

• IMPROVED! LOGIN – Quick and easy login using Touch ID / Face ID (iPhone X family) features.

• NEW AND IMPROVED! MANAGE YOUR ACCOUNTS – View your Relationship Rewards level and benefits, your account balances and transaction history, transfer money between your accounts, and much more!

• NEW AND IMPROVED! PAY YOUR BILLS – Sign up for Bill Pay right from your phone and add & manage your payees wherever you are. It's a cinch to view your bills, schedule payments, or make a payment on the go.

• IMPROVED! MAKE DEPOSITS – Our mobile app makes it easy for you to make deposits everywhere you are. We'll take the picture for you!

• NEW AND IMPROVED! VIEW CHECKS - Now you can view checks you have deposited in app in your checking account. You can now also view any check written from your account!

• NEW! E-STATEMENTS - View your statements from this year and last year.

• NEW AND IMPROVED! FICO® - View your current FICO® score and now you can view your previous FICO® scores to better understand your credit history.

• MESSAGE CENTER – Provides a secure messaging area where you can connect with us to get assistance.

• CARD CONTROLS – Provides an option to lock/unlock your credit cards.

• LOCATIONS – Find nearby branches and ATMs using built-in GPS. Additionally, you can search by zip code or address.

• TRANSFER FUNDS – Real-time money transfers between your accounts or schedule transfers for a future date.

VIEW YOUR FICO® SCORE
FICO® Scores are the credit scores used by 90% of top lenders to determine your credit risk. Now you can view your FICO® Score and key factors impacting your score right from the app in the menu. (Note: FICO® Scores are available to Members with at least one of the following: checking account, loan product, or credit card.)

OTHER UPDATES
• We've updated our feedback features. Tell us how we can improve!
• We've addressed a few other minor bugs.

Thanks for being a Partners Member!

There's a lot of backstage changes in this version, which is getting us ready for some big updates. Stay tuned!

Also,
• We've added the ability to send in-app notifications. Stay on top of the latest updates on your finances, nearby branches, and any other important events!
• As always, we made a few minor improvements and bug fixes here and there too.

Thank you for being a Partners Member!

We have fixed a few bugs and made a few small improvements:

• We fixed a rare bug where the app would temporarily not remember your login details
• We made a small improvement with Mobile Check Deposit
• And a few other small fixes

Thank you for being a Partners Member!

What's new in version 6.3:

VIEW ROUTING AND MEMBERSHIP NUMBERS
• Now you can view your membership and routing numbers right in the app!
• Just select SETTINGS / INFO from the menu. The routing number is shown. Tap the VIEW link for your membership number

VIEW ACCOUNT NUMBERS
• View the associated account number or account ID for your accounts.
• Just tap the VIEW link when viewing your account details.
• NOTE: For security purposes Credit and Debit Cards are excluded.

Thank you VERY MUCH for being a Partners Member!

Partners Mobile Banking 6.3.2 includes:
• Enhanced compatibility with iOS 12.
• Some small bug fixes.

Thank you very much for being a Partners Member!

• We've fixed the display issue with transactions and removed all of the extra white space.
• Plus a few other smaller bugs

Thank you for being a Partners Member!
